com.ibm.ccl.soa.core.saf.ui.handler
Interface IInterfaceDescriptionProvider

public interface IInterfaceDescriptionProvider

The IInterfaceDescriptionProvider maps an interface object to an optional image and optional text string used to display the element in the viewer's control.
